{"name": "django-simple-captcha", "metadata": {"name": "django-simple-captcha", "version": "0.6.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Environment :: Web Environment", "Framework :: Django", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP", "Topic :: Security"], "home_page": "https://github.com/mbi/django-simple-captcha", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["Django", "Pillow", "django-ranged-response"], "summary": "A very simple, yet powerful, Django captcha application", "upload_time": 1701703683}, "documentation": ["# Django Simple Captcha\n\n```{image} https://github.com/mbi/django-simple-captcha/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg\n:target: https://github.com/mbi/django-simple-captcha/actions/workflows/test.yml\n```\n\n```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/django-simple-captcha\n:target: https://pypi.org/project/django-simple-captcha/\n```\n\n```{image} https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/django-simple-captcha\n:target: https://github.com/mbi/django-simple-captcha/blob/master/LICENSE\n```\n\nDjango Simple Captcha is an extremely simple, yet highly customizable Django application to add captcha images to any Django form.\n\n```{image} http://django-simple-captcha.readthedocs.io/en/latest/_images/captcha3.png\n```\n\n## Features\n\n- Very simple to setup and deploy, yet very configurable\n- Can use custom challenges (e.g. random chars, simple math, dictionary word, ...)\n- Custom generators, noise and filter functions alter the look of the generated image\n- Supports text-to-speech audio output of the challenge text, for improved accessibility\n- Ajax refresh\n\n## Requirements\n\n- Django 4.2+, Python3.8+\n- A recent version of the Pillow compiled with FreeType support\n- Flite is required for text-to-speech (audio) output, but not mandatory\n\n## Documentation\n\nRead the [documentation online](http://django-simple-captcha.readthedocs.org/en/latest/).\n"], "modules": [{"name": "captcha.helpers", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "captcha.helpers.math_challenge", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.random_char_challenge", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.unicode_challenge", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.word_challenge", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.huge_words_and_punctuation_challenge", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.noise_arcs", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "draw", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "image", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.noise_dots", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "draw", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "image", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.noise_null", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "draw", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "image", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.post_smooth", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "image", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.captcha_image_url", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "key", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Return url to image. Need for ajax refresh and, etc"]}, {"name": "captcha.helpers.captcha_audio_url",